Author: gaborcselle
Content: Interesting side note: Zingy was founded in NYC by Fabrice Grinda, a French guy (http://fabricegrinda.com/) He had previously started Aucland in France, an Alando competitor. It's a small world. He'd be a great candidate for a Euro edition of "Founders at Work".
